{"tid":2514213,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 敲定回歸日期！迷你十輯在美國與全球分別發行","createTime":"2021-05-03T06:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T09:37:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a361c21b0802eb9fdb44dd3d2d41049b9d46fd","tid":2514213,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"上個月就搶先預告回歸消息的 TWICE 今天宣布了正式的日期，這次她們特地為美國訂出了另外的發片日！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 今天（3 日）公開了 TWICE 第十張迷你專輯〈Taste of Love〉的預告照，並宣布她們將於 6 月 9、11 兩日分別在全球（美國除外）及美國發片，即日起就能開始預購這張新專輯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_894666d92d12f6b7c35caf92fe1f9958/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-05-03/135246-905208.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_894666d92d12f6b7c35caf92fe1f9958%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-05-03%2F135246-905208.jpeg&h=3fad6a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTWICE 的上一張作品是去年 10 月推出的正規二輯〈Eyes wide open〉，這段時間她們除了在韓國年末頒獎典禮上公開新歌外，也發行了久違的英語單曲和日語單曲，同時活躍在各國。<br />\n<br />\n特別的是，TWICE 近期也登上了美國電視節目《The Kelly Clarkson Show》，越來越深入當地市場，新專輯〈Taste of Love〉將在當地獲得的迴響也因此備受關注！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"6b0fe1e6b41ace19aa6a4f2dd389ab5221d32150","tid":2514213,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"定仔回歸未"},{"pid":"ffa082ec8cbc4a0161a505a1b8d184ac7e274df6","tid":2514213,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"牙腸留幾多做爆碟基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de906e55c193e12fb336d9de0be00aacf2f87bc","tid":2514213,"uid":80047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:25:39.000Z","msg":"希望小隊大解開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f2823dd8ce22944aaf7d9832153ad63083